==How to install==

To install theme, move RLight-WP folder or clone the repo to

<pre>
/path/to/blog/wp-content/themes/
</pre>

Theme will need to be activated for theme to be usable.

==Misc.==

This project is meant to provide a good basis for a wordpress theme, and was tested on version 4.9.5.

Things should '''mostly''' work right, but there may be things missing, so the theme is not exactly complete.

You can use this a theme, or to make a semidescent starting point.